beer.beer_description:
First brewed for 2016 GABS Festival.
This American IPA fermented with 100% brettanomyces yeast is a knockout of tropical pineapple, mango, peach, citrus and funky brett.
With an addition of oatmeal, this beer has a silky smooth mouthfeel and a hint of sweetness.
